crudPickerPanelDef

public static <K extends Serializable & Comparable<? super K>,PO extends PersistentObject<K>,KQ extends Question<K> & PoDependent<PO>> CrudPickerPanelDef<PO> crudPickerPanelDef(Class<PO> poClass,
                                                                                                                                                                               Class<KQ> questionClass)
Creates a CrudPickerPanelDefinition for a CrudPickerPanel. The definition created by this method does not have a back action or a pick action. It also does not have any PanelCreator or DataTableCreator. These properties of the SearchFlowPanelDef must be filled manually. The same goes for the wicket id and the list of the table elements to be shown in the panel.

Type Parameters:
K - Type of persistent object key.
PO - Type of persistent object.
KQ - Type of next key question.
Parameters:
poClass - Class of PersistentObject.
questionClass - Type of next key question.
Returns:
Returns a CrudPickerPanelDef.
